    <main role="main">
      <h1>Proposed SEI Website Navigation</h1>
      <p class="small">Aspirational information architecture with copy placements derived from the Beth &amp; Xiao conversation.</p>

      <div class="hr"></div>

      <h2>Top-Level Navigation</h2>
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Home</h3>
          <p><strong>Hero message:</strong> “We connect classrooms, campuses, and communities to make sustainability a living part of education.”</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Gateway: Faculty Development → <em>Programs &amp; Learning</em></li>
            <li>Gateway: Student Opportunities → <em>Internships &amp; Projects</em></li>
            <li>Gateway: Partnerships in Action → <em>Partnerships &amp; Impact</em></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Programs &amp; Learning</h3>
          <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Faculty-centered professional development ecosystem.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Faculty Professional Development</li>
            <li>Workshops &amp; Demonstration Projects</li>
            <li>Curriculum Support &amp; Resources</li>
          </ul>
          <blockquote>We’re the in-house professional development organizers and hosts — the only group doing this district-wide.</blockquote>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Student Opportunities</h3>
          <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Internship and experiential learning hub.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Internships through Build LACCD</li>
            <li>Learning from the Campus Itself (living labs)</li>
            <li>How to Get Involved / Apply</li>
          </ul>
          <blockquote>From 9 to 100+ internships — linking learning to real jobs.</blockquote>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Partnerships &amp; Impact</h3>
          <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Elevates collaborations and policy leadership.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Campus &amp; Facilities Collaborations</li>
            <li>Community &amp; Policy Work</li>
            <li>Networks &amp; Partners (Climate Center, UCLA, ASCCC, Indigenous communities, legislators)</li>
          </ul>
          <blockquote>We bridge operations and education — making sustainability part of how campuses are built and maintained.</blockquote>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Events &amp; News</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Upcoming Workshops / Professional Development</li>
            <li>Recent Highlights &amp; Press</li>
            <li>Community Features (students, faculty, policy wins)</li>
          </ul>
          <blockquote>Our workshops reach staff, faculty, students — and the wider community.</blockquote>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Resources</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Toolkits &amp; Curriculum Guides</li>
            <li>Recorded Webinars &amp; Past Workshops</li>
            <li>Research &amp; Policy Links</li>
            <li>Newsletter Archive</li>
          </ul>
          <blockquote>We’re the place faculty go for practical and theoretical ideas.</blockquote>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>About</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Mission &amp; Vision</li>
            <li>Who We Are</li>
            <li>Our Story</li>
            <li>Contact &amp; Get Involved</li>
          </ul>
          <blockquote>It’s important that we exist — and that people understand what we do and why it matters.</blockquote>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Gold Creek</h3>
          <p>Dedicated destination for field-based learning and community research.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Cross-link from Student Opportunities</li>
            <li>Cross-link from Programs &amp; Learning</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hr"></div>

      <h2>Copy Segments</h2>
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>About SEI</h3>
          <blockquote>SEI leads faculty professional development and curriculum innovation in sustainability and environmental education across the district.”
          </blockquote>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Our Impact</h3>
          <blockquote>From policy advocacy to campus design, SEI bridges classrooms, operations, and community action.</blockquote>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Faculty &amp; Curriculum</h3>
          <blockquote>We train, support, and inspire faculty to integrate environmental equity into every discipline.</blockquote>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Student Opportunities</h3>
          <blockquote>SEI connects students to paid internships and real-world sustainability projects across the region.</blockquote>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Community Engagement</h3>
          <blockquote>We host workshops, build partnerships, and support community resilience through environmental learning.</blockquote>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Policy &amp; Partnerships</h3>
          <blockquote>SEI collaborates with facilities, legislators, and statewide organizations to advance sustainability policy and practice.</blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="small">IA draft for browser review and stakeholder feedback.</p>

